LANG_ENGLISH        "Great, looks like somebody's home.  Luke sure knows how to pick 'em.  We'll set down in that canyon and try to sneak into the castle."
LANG_CZECH        "Vyborne, vypada to, ze je nekdo doma.  Luke vazne vi kde je hledat. Pristaneme dole v kanonu a pokusime se proplizit do pevnosti."

REFERENCE           17KYK006
LANG_ENGLISH        "Great, looks like somebody's home.  Luke sure knows how to pick 'em.  We'll set down there at the base of the castle.  "
LANG_CZECH        "Vyborne, vypada to, ze je nekdo doma.  Luke vazne vi kde je hledat.  Pristaneme dole na nadvori pevnosti."

REFERENCE           17KYK007
NOTES               "(in pain)"
LANG_ENGLISH        "Argh!  This rain's like acid!  Find some cover, fast!"
LANG_CZECH        "Aaah!  Ten dest je jako kyselina! Najdi nejaky ukryt, rychle!"

REFERENCE           17KYK008
LANG_ENGLISH        "We're gonna have to run from cover to cover.  You've learned how to Protect yourself using the Force.  Use it so the rain doesn't hit you."
LANG_CZECH        "Budeme muset behat z ukrytu do ukrytu.  Naucil jsi se jak se chranit pomoci Sily. Pouzij ji, dest te nezasahne."

REFERENCE           17KYK009
LANG_ENGLISH        "We're gonna have to run from cover to cover.  Keep out of the rain as much as possible."
LANG_CZECH        "Budeme muset behat z ukrytu do ukrytu.  Vyhybej se desti, jak jen to bude mozne."

REFERENCE           17KYK010
LANG_ENGLISH        "Looks like the welcome wagon's arrived."
LANG_CZECH        "Vypada to, ze uvitaci vybor dorazil."

REFERENCE           17KYK011
LANG_ENGLISH        "What are these things?"
LANG_CZECH        "Co je to zac?"

REFERENCE           17KYK012
