LANG_ENGLISH        "Must be some kind of trooper designed for nasty environments like this."
LANG_CZECH        "Musi to byt nejaky druh vojaku stvorenych pro podobna prostredi, jako je tohle."

REFERENCE           17KYK013
LANG_ENGLISH        "I say we try to avoid this garrison.  Our objective is the castle."
LANG_CZECH        "Rekl jsem, abychom se pokusili vyhnout kasarnam. Nasim cilem je pevnost."

REFERENCE           17KYK014
LANG_ENGLISH        "Take cover!"
LANG_CZECH        "Kryj se!"

REFERENCE           17KYK015
LANG_ENGLISH        "Guess they're expecting us now..."
LANG_CZECH        "Ted uz nas asi ocekavaji..."

REFERENCE           17KYK016
